# Project Overview: Modelman (xomda.js)

**xomda.js** is a full-stack TypeScript monorepo for data model design and code generation. It enables users to design database schemas visually and automatically generate code artifacts from customizable cell-based templates (logic / handlebars / output / provider cells).

## Core Purpose

1. **Data Modeling** - Design entities and attributes interactively
2. **Code Generation** - Generate code via cell-based templates (`.template.json`)
3. **Type-Safe APIs** - Client-server communication via tRPC with full type safety
4. **Visual Editing** - Interactive diagram-based UI for entity visualization

